data.description: Custom-built Contemporary home on 2 acres with beautiful view of Angel's Rest Mountain. Hardwood floors throughout with formal sunken Living Room,  Family Room w/brick hearth/woodstove, built-in entertainment center & large windows provide lots of natural light! Great Kitchen w/tile backsplash, island, pantry, cherry cabinets & more! Large Laundry on main. Master Bedroom has two walk-in closets and French doors leading to adjoining Study. Two heat pumps. Attached Double Garage w/concrete circular drive. Two nice storage rooms.  SELLER IS OFFERING $5,000 TOWARD PURCHASER'S CLOSING COSTS!
